alue":"Knowledge can be viewed at different levels of granularity depending on the user's expertise."}],"http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label":[{"@value":"Knowledge representation granularity"}],"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel":[{"@value":"Knowledge representation granularity"}],"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type":[{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/mco/Topic"}]},{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/meetgraph/meeting/11","https://tekrajchhetri.com/mco/has_topic":[{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/meetgraph/meeting/11/topic/6"}]},{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/meetgraph/meeting/11/topic/6","http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAttributedTo":[{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/meetgraph/meeting/11/agent/tek-raj-chhetri"}],"https://tekrajchhetri.com/mco/point":[{"@value":"The discussion mentioned a user interface intended to allow searching different items, but the transcript cuts off before specifying what is searched."}],"http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label":[{"@value":"User interface search capability"}],"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel":[{"@value":"User interface search capability"}],"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type":[{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/mco/Topic"}]},{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/meetgraph/meeting/11","https://tekrajchhetri.com/mco/has_topic":[{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/meetgraph/meeting/11/topic/5"}]},{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/meetgraph/meeting/11/topic/5","http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasAttributedTo":[{"@id":"https://tekrajchhetri.com/meetgraph/meeting/11/agent/tek-raj-chhetri"}],"https://tekrajchhetri.com/mco/point":[{"@value":"The work also includes creating the infrastructure."},{"@value":"The work includes collecting literature, synthesizing it, running automated extraction, and validating the extraction."}],"http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label":[{"@value":"Literature synthesis and extraction workflow"}],"http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel":[{"@valu